  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Happy Numbers</strong> is a relaxing, mind-blending, minimalist puzzle game that offer over 70 hand-crafted levels to immerse your self into. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420830/extras/6417d60462b927d9a71f3413912742f9.poster.avif?t=1729179400\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420830/extras/6417d60462b927d9a71f3413912742f9.webm?t=1729179400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420830/extras/6417d60462b927d9a71f3413912742f9.mp4?t=1729179400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also constain a lot of beautiful characters to unlock. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let's train your brain and get the beautiful girls. YAY!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to play:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❥ Fill the grid by mouse dragging over cells with a number inside. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❥ Green highlighted indicates that you can slide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❥ Red highlighted indicates indicates you cannot slide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to play but not easy to win. Let's try it out !!!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Happy Numbers</strong> is a relaxing, mind-blending, minimalist puzzle game that offer over 70 hand-crafted levels to immerse your self into. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420830/extras/6417d60462b927d9a71f3413912742f9.poster.avif?t=1729179400\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420830/extras/6417d60462b927d9a71f3413912742f9.webm?t=1729179400\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1420830/extras/6417d60462b927d9a71f3413912742f9.mp4?t=1729179400\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also constain a lot of beautiful characters to unlock. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Let's train your brain and get the beautiful girls. YAY!!!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How to play:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❥ Fill the grid by mouse dragging over cells with a number inside. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❥ Green highlighted indicates that you can slide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >❥ Red highlighted indicates indicates you cannot slide.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to play but not easy to win. Let's try it out !!!</p>",
